<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Third_Punic_War&amp;action=edit"><abbr title="Edit this template" style=";background-color:#B0C4DE;;background:none transparent;border:none;">e</abbr></a></li>
