<li><a href="/wiki/Lelantine_War" title="Lelantine War">Lelantine War</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Greek%E2%80%93Punic_Wars" title="Greek–Punic Wars" class="mw-redirect">Greek–Punic Wars (Sicilian Wars)</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Greco-Persian_Wars" title="Greco-Persian Wars">Greco-Persian Wars</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Aegina#Rivalry_with_Athens_.285th_century_BC.29" title="Aegina">Aeginetan War</a></li>
